high_descs: walk over to the front of the sink
pick up the mug from the sink
take the mug over to the front of the fridge
put the mug in the fridge for a few moments then remove
take the mug to the counter to the right of the sink
put the mug under the coffee machine
anns.task_desc: chill a mug in the fridge and place it under the machine

high_descs: Turn right and walk to the left side of the sink and face it.
Pick up the mug from the left side of the sink.
Turn right and walk to the fridge and face it.
Chill the mug in the fridge then get it back out and close the door.
Turn left and walk all the way to the coffee maker on the left side of the room and stand facing it.
Put the mug under the coffee makers spout.
anns.task_desc: Put a cold mug under the coffee maker.

high_descs: Turn right, walk to the sink on the right.
Pick up the black coffee mug to the right of the spatula.
Turn right, walk to the fridge on the left.
Put the mug on the second shelf in the fridge, close the door, let the mug chill, take the mug out of the fridge, and close the door.
Turn left and walk to the coffee maker on the counter to the left of the stove.
Place the black mug in the coffee maker.
anns.task_desc: To chill a mug and put it in a coffee maker.
